  "body": "<img alt=\"10a-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2d7f3471d5b9dc1d.jpg?v=1782533126\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"10b-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/12da7810d2b9e84f.jpg?v=1782533128\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10c-Los+Angeles+Clear+Stamps+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7d1ce09ed563da65.jpg?v=1782533131\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>These are the Los Angeles stamps.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"10g-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b68ce3321ad9e7f9.jpg?v=1782533134\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10d-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/36edc534bae94164.jpg?v=1782533137\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10e-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/52e07c10fb8189de.jpg?v=1782533140\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10h-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c39bb12733a7f854.jpg?v=1782533142\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10f-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/adbd547ba9864750.jpg?v=1782533145\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10i-Summer+Clear+Stamps+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/55589be289027c88.jpg?v=1782533148\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10j-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/27131b8a46ce6929.jpg?v=1782533150\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10k-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/160d075a7fb1ff9e.jpg?v=1782533153\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10l-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6ca0412f03922b35.jpg?v=1782533156\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10m-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/749842890380f6ce.jpg?v=1782533159\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10n-New+Stamps!+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/47391f4951f9604e.jpg?v=1782533162\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>These were so fun to work on in the studio! And admittedly, we have gone a bit flamingo crazy. If you have the set from <a href=\"http://whimsodoodle.com/\">Whim So Doodle</a> and you get both of these brand new limited edition sets, you will have all three and they are all different. The sets are 4x6 photopolymer clear stamps and made in the USA. Grab them while you can in <a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/shop/?category=Paper+Products\">the shop</a>!</p>"
